		<description>A squad support electromagnetic-propelled grenade launcher designed for long-range engagements. Capable of firing low-accuracy high-explosive grenades in bursts for suppressive fire, or single-shot EMP grenades with enhanced precision. The dual drum magazine system allows rapid ammunition switching to adapt to combat scenarios.\n\nThis weapon can fire over obstacles, but cannot automatically target enemies outside the operator's line of sight.\n\nThis heavy weapon system can be disabled in mod settings. However, due to its high production cost, it may not spawn naturally in standard raid events even with generation options enabled.</description>
